name: Iphone Unlock Iphone 4/4S 3/3GS GSM Only
description:
All you need to do is provide us with the imei number for your phone and we will unlock it.

The IMEI number is found by going to your "SETTINGS" > "GENERAL" > "ABOUT" > "IMEI"

Please send us the imei message via Contact, or invoice when purchasing item.

The Unlocking Process may Take up to 1 Day.

Once we have confirmed your phone as Unlocked, You just need to restore your phone or put different sim card in.

Payment can be done via paypal or 
"Credit card if you do not have a paypal"
